            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "第一红宝石",
            "Text": "……",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "第一红宝石",
            "Text": "……麻烦你了。",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "第一红宝石",
            "Text": "……",
            "ChoiceDataList": [
                "呃，不对！刚刚那是……！"
            ],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "",
            "Text": "不知为何，我竟然凭空说出想都没想的话……！\n我陷入慌乱，赶紧努力圆回来──",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
