        },
        {
            "Name": "大拓太阳神",
            "Text": "对啦────────！！",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "大拓太阳神",
            "Text": "太强了！\n我的心声直接传到你脑海了☆",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
