            "Text": "……哭哭？",
            "ChoiceDataList": [
                "爆哭……"
            ],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        },
        {
            "Name": "",
            "Text": "经过这个新年，\n我跟大拓太阳神之间……\n似乎萌生了同伴情谊？",
            "ChoiceDataList": [],
            "ColorTextInfoList": []
        }
